{"tid":1291190,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今日屯公一役見到藍絲內鬨","createTime":"2019-07-06T18:34:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-06T19:16:39.000Z","uid":248695,"like":70,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f8509c764f638d63941481a706f3502b4e601ab3","tid":1291190,"uid":248695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T18:34:57.000Z","msg":"港人講地個賤post又借啲意抽水話我哋係暴徒<br />\n<br />\n但屯門區居民好支持我哋今次行動<br />\n<br />\n結果屯門藍絲同死硬派藍絲開始互屌，一邊撐我哋一邊繼續盲反<br />\n<br />\n民意從來都係爭取行益最大嘅本錢，既然政府唔就5點作出回應，我希望未來會有更加多嘅光復行動，俾香港市民知道我哋唔係要分藍黃，做嘅呢一切係為有一個更好嘅香港<br />\n<br />\n巴打絲打加油，我哋要繼續努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"914b2fbca4b55415c2d1baaf2f1fa73768bea0ba","tid":1291190,"uid":72240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T18:37:10.000Z","msg":"香港人要團結<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9324b36f80d3a7ccd764c0cc70d04455398e7eb1","tid":1291190,"uid":11148,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T18:38:07.000Z","msg":"啱，6國畀暴秦所滅階因被分化而不能團結<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26eb78c982c02d2ab42289ea735af554684dc38a","tid":1291190,"uid":23189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"914b2fbca4b55415c2d1baaf2f1fa73768bea0ba","tid":1291190,"uid":72240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T18:37:10.000Z","msg":"香港人要團結<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T18:38:46.000Z","msg":"幫屯門藍屌鳩其他藍<br />\n拉攏佢哋去我哋陣營<br />\n<br />\n________________________<br />\n黑衫口罩作記認<br />\n一. 可以掩飾身份<br />\n二. 響街度可以幫返自己人<br />\n<br />\n「七黑」團結打倒白色恐怖<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1284973\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1284973</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zm1ytZc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?